---
// Purpose-Built Capabilities section for CRE industry page
---

<section id="capabilities" class="cre-capabilities-section">
  <div class="cre-capabilities-container">
    <span class="section-label">PURPOSE-BUILT CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="cre-capabilities-headline">
      CRE systems engineered for your workflow
    </h2>

    <div class="cre-capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Deal Sourcing -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-1.webp" alt="Deal Sourcing" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Deal Sourcing</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Unified platform that aggregates deals from brokers, off-market sources, and your network into a single pipeline. Track deal status, source quality, and response times in real-time.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Broker network integration</li>
            <li>Deal pipeline tracking</li>
            <li>Source performance analytics</li>
            <li>Automated deal alerts</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Underwriting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-5.webp" alt="Underwriting" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Underwriting</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated underwriting workflows that pull data from property records, market comps, and financial models—reducing analysis time from days to hours while improving accuracy.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated financial modeling</li>
            <li>Market comp analysis</li>
            <li>Risk assessment tools</li>
            <li>Deal comparison dashboards</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Analytics -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-6.webp" alt="Portfolio Analytics" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Portfolio Analytics</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Real-time portfolio performance tracking across all properties. Monitor occupancy, NOI, cap rates, and asset-level metrics in a single dashboard.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Portfolio-wide performance metrics</li>
            <li>Asset-level analytics</li>
            <li>Occupancy and lease tracking</li>
            <li>Performance forecasting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Investor Reporting -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-2.webp" alt="Investor Reporting" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Investor Reporting</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Automated investor reports that generate on-demand or on-schedule. Pull data from your portfolio systems and deliver formatted reports to investors without manual work.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Automated report generation</li>
            <li>Custom report templates</li>
            <li>Investor portal access</li>
            <li>Historical reporting archive</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Buyer Profile Management -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-3.webp" alt="Buyer Profile Management" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Buyer Profile Management</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Centralized system for tracking buyer preferences, deal history, and relationship management. Match deals to buyers automatically based on criteria and past behavior.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Buyer preference tracking</li>
            <li>Deal matching algorithms</li>
            <li>Relationship management tools</li>
            <li>Communication history</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Market Intelligence -->
      <div class="cre-capability-card">
        <div class="cre-capability-icon">
          <img src="/logos/intelio-icon-7.webp" alt="Market Intelligence" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="cre-capability-title">Market Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="cre-capability-description">
          Aggregated market data, news, and trends that surface automatically. Get alerts on market shifts, new opportunities, and competitive intelligence relevant to your portfolio.
        </p>
        <div class="cre-includes-section">
          <strong>INCLUDES:</strong>
          <ul class="cre-includes-list">
            <li>Market trend analysis</li>
            <li>News and alert aggregation</li>
            <li>Competitive intelligence</li>
            <li>Opportunity identification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-capabilities-section {
    background: #0052CC;
    color: #ffffff;
    width: 100vw;
    margin: 0;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    padding: clamp(40px, 5vw, 60px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .cre-capability-card {
    background: transparent;
    border: 3px solid #ffffff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cre-capability-icon img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .cre-capability-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }

  .cre-capability-description {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .cre-includes-section strong {
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-includes-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 4px 0 4px 16px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .cre-includes-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-capabilities-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-capabilities-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-capability-card {
      padding: 28px 20px;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
    }

    .cre-capability-icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .cre-capability-title {
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cre-capability-description {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cre-includes-list li {
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>

